extendedInfo.description: Find nearby parking locations in NYC, Boston, Philadelphia, Washington DC and over 40 other cities (listed below). The Central Parking app allows you to easily find parking using your location or by custom search and provides useful information for each Central Parking location including hours of operation, rates, available discounts, phone number and more. Top Features Include:*National Footprintâ Parking locations available in over 50 cities nationwide including NYC, Boston, Philadelphia, Washington DC, Chicago, Denver, Los Angeles, San Francisco and more* Parking Locatorâ Find a selection of parking facilities near your exact location using GPS technology that automatically identifies the locations (on GPS enabled devices only)* Parking Searchâ Find a selection of parking facilities near a specific address you are planning to visit through custom search capabilities.* Take Me There - Get turn-by-turn directions to Central Parking locations from your current location using your phone's native navigation app* Mobile Coupons: Create coupons and get discounts directly from your device for select locations. (**availability varies per city and per location. Must pay with credit card to receive discounted rate)* Favorites: Easily save your favorite locations so you can create your mobile coupon even quicker than before!* Text N Go: Send an SMS to eligible locations to let the attendant know what time your car should be ready for you to pick up... straight from our app! * Where I Parked: Easily mark on the map the location you parked your car at.  You can then use the app to quickly get directions to and from the location.Parking Locations Available In:    New York, NY    Boston, MA    Philadelphia, PA    Washington DC    Chicago, IL    Albuquerque, NM    Atlanta, GA    Austin, TX    Baltimore, MD    Birmingham, AL    Charlotte, NC    Cleveland, OH    Columbia, SC    Columbus, OH    Dallas, TX    Denver, CO    Detroit, MI    Greenville, SC    Hartford, CT    Houston, TX    Jacksonville, FL    Kansas City, MO    Knoxville, TN    Lexington, KY    Los Angeles, CA    Memphis, TN    Miami, FL    Milwaukee, WI    Minneapolis, MN    Mobile, AL    Nashville, TN    New Orleans, LA    Oakland, CA    Oklahoma City, OK    Omaha, NE    Orlando, FL    Phoenix, AZ    Pittsburgh, PA    Providence, RI    Richmond, VA    San Antonio, TX    San Diego, CA    San Francisco, CA    San Jose, CA    Seattle, WA    St. Louis, MO    Syracuse, NY    Tampa, FL    Tulsa, OK    Wilmington, DE    Winston-Salem, NC

reviews.title: All right, but lacking
reviews.comment: Rates are not displayed in the map and list views, you need to check each location individually. Also, it requires registration. The app for Icon Parking is much more usable.
reviews.author: Bogdan Calmac

reviews.title: Horrible
reviews.comment: After logging out of the app it wont let me log back in.  Crapppp
reviews.author: Mohamed Eisa

reviews.title: Ever heard of electronic coupons?
reviews.comment: Good for what it can do, but it mystifies me why vendor still insists that most coupons are printed out, rendering the app useless for most discounts.
reviews.author: Harold Goldner

reviews.title: Saved $$!
reviews.comment: Used the mobile coupon. After 3x it was recognized by their system. Highly recommended if you drive in NYC. Valet parking at the hotel would have been $65+. We paid $55 for 30 hours.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Saved me a lot of money
reviews.comment: It worked great. I was able to find alternate parking when I was in central Philly for much cheaper than the valet parking at the hotel I stayed at. The app shows a list of all their parking garages as well as rates and discounts. I would give five stars if some locations did not require you to print the coupon. There should be a discount code you can present to the parking attendant.
reviews.author: Terelle Dorceus

reviews.title: Cr\'app
reviews.comment: Never sent the confirmation e-mail, so couldn\'t use. Waste of time.
reviews.author: David Hatch-Bernier

reviews.title: Terrible service, scary place to go
reviews.comment: Central parking pay machines rip you off!! Avoid any of there parking garages.

reviews.title: Very easy to use.
reviews.comment: Quick and very responsive app. Love it.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Save a ton on parking with coupons!
reviews.comment: Central has mobile coupons available for most of the locations I use in NYC.  Fast and convenient and I have saved up to $20 off the posted rates.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Parking finder with discounts
reviews.comment: Love the app - I use the Central website to get coupons - the app also allows me to find parking near me and get discounts from my phone.  That said, there are some locations that do require a printed coupon which gets emailed to you, but the app is pretty clear about which is which.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Tried entering my address, it couldn\'t find the garage I gave because my GPS is off. Website is terrible too. Im not giving these guys any more money.
